s, debug artifacts, or missing files\n4. If anything fails: one retry via Gemini, then do it yourself\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5e9ccb72-92b1-4105-bb6a-f0ce0b7c984f","uuid":"434b02bb-661d-40cf-8d1a-d60f2629547d","isSynthetic":true}
